Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.50,0:01:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.44,0:01:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.28,0:01:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以为王子的置物箱一定能看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.41,0:01:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想看什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漫画里不是常看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一打开置物箱 巧克力就霹雳啪拉地掉出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在真实生活中应该不会发生那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.82,0:01:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这应该是和布谷鸟幼鸟同样的行为造成的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布谷鸟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像布谷鸟会把伯劳鸟的蛋从鸟巢推下去一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少女们为了让你一眼看到她的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会把先放进来的巧克力给丢掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,证据就在那个垃圾桶里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.21,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 好过分哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想夺取最后一个巧克力的那只老鹰就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃吧 巧克力罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那是由希的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是二月14日情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.14,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一大早就展现出他的战斗心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要送给草摩同学的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.11,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧克力是要送给…草摩同学的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学…\N由希同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时下的女孩真是可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仿佛会突然从街角冲过去似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.15,0:03:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于十二生肖的男孩们来说 或许这是最可怕的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.09,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是送给小鱼和小花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每年都麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好高兴 你想要什么回礼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用什么回礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老是在麻烦你们 这个就算是谢礼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送你巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 阿夹好受欢迎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.55,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生意不错哦 连阿夹都这么热门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.35,0:03:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是情人节啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 家里也很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旅行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 出去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要暂时消失一阵子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.29,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 我的最爱～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她真的来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不想见乐罗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为今天是情人节啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是情侣们重要的节日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁跟谁是情侣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.41,0:04:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你别乱插嘴 不然家里会被拆掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该早点出去旅行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到今天居然是情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.75,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人都会知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你送他巧克力了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为阿夹太害羞了 一直都不肯收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情人节快乐 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装满了我今年对你的爱的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人哪会吃那种甜死人的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.37,0:05:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啊 原来阿夹讨厌巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 最讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别讲一大堆歪理了 我叫你吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你吃\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快吃\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快吃！\N不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你该不会也准备了巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.73,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我是准备送给大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该先问一下大家喜不喜欢吃巧克力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒很想…想吃小透的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而这个送给紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你早就想要了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我一直受你们照顾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.26,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里…我哪有照顾你什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 我真的好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透爱的巧克力抚平了我身心的疲惫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不嫌弃的话 乐罗也来一个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有啊 好高兴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.82,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有波鸟、泼春、红叶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.75,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好是能亲手拿给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到你准备得还真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为包装得很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以忍不住就买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.43,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 我却不知道他们喜不喜欢巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别理会阿夹说的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.41,0:07:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些能大言不惭地说出"身为男人"这种话的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实根本是不了解真正的"男子气概"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随意践踏"人的心"和"人的爱"的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.55,0:07:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说是当男人了 连当人的资格都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我不应该买巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而应该选像"拳头仙贝"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是"雷饼"这类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比较有男子气概的点心才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些也挺好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃就是了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹吃我的巧克力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.75,0:07:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了 我会再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 阿春告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和由希和好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.99,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还说只要你们更了解对方 感情搞不好会更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能这样的话 我也会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小波 我送你的情人节巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我骗你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小透送你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.95,0:08:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人的份也都托我拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情人节就这样子度过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间到了 大家把笔放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后一个月的时间过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转眼间期末考也结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然考试很辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但考试结束时的解脱感是我最爱的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 我考得很好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我平常还答得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你考得不错啊 那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.23,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要肯努力 小透也一样办得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为由希肯教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a7\fs22}只\N是\N来\N捣\N蛋\N的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他自己也要温书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却还仔细解说 只为了让我听懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里 你太夸张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学…他笑得好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么 他们到底在讲什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个电波女人太可怕 害我们无法靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.73,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花岛同学 你好像很会念书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有电波 感觉又很有知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上学期的期末考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.87,0:10:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你平均考了几分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.34,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想想 那时候我每天接受辅导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父母都被找来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 我妈妈还哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 你电波的威力呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.15,0:10:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说我笨的程度连电波也无法弥补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.06,0:10:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 花岛 还有人比你更笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.63,0:10:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你不会是指我吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,废话 当然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从来没接受过课后辅导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父母也没被找来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹其实功课不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 什么叫"其实"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是不在乎输赢吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这跟那没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.52,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 其实你是那种每天孜孜不倦K著书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果却念错考试范围 自我爆炸型的笨蛋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么一猜就中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.16,0:11:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近他老关在房间里 原来就是在念书啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.90,0:11:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一想到他勤奋念书的模样就不禁叫人莞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过阿夹还是活蹦乱跳的模样比较适合他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田 你来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会好好打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打工 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久没看到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期末考考完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 今天开始我会努力工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮了大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.54,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是刚来 快点进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.78,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都这么晚了 还这么有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是第一次来小紫家 好兴奋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死人的人又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 刚洗完澡很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的好精神就是叫我不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:13:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹在欺负人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶 肚子饿不饿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这点叫我不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.61,0:13:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶 你说了今天来住这里的原因了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有问题问小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.62,0:13:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是几月几日呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.16,0:13:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是…三月14日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三月14日是White day
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以明天我要回礼给你 送你温泉旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.91,0:13:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旅行的名称就是"我和小透两人的温泉之旅"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用取名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里的温泉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是草摩家经营的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温泉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.75,0:13:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招待我去那种高级的场所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.92,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说太奢侈了 我一定会遭天谴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 只不过是温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是要请你去巴黎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拒绝的话太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就趁这个机会消除一下家事和打工的疲劳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道小透你不高兴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴 我好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希和阿夹也要一起去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这小鬼 怎么擅自决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去嘛 一起去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别搞错了 我是不会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会去 难得有这机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就更不会去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钱的问题你别担心 我存了很多零用钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是钱的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 讲到钱…小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说你上个月的旅行基金还没交啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到你班导师电话的爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打电话跟我说他要帮你付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.92,0:15:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行的 不行 真的不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上个月因为很多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我这个月拿到薪水就会付清了 别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经告诉导师了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 让你们担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.81,0:15:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你上个月明明有打工 为什么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是拿去买情人节的巧克力了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 学期旅行要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…快去…洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佩服佩服 你还真能忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧克力不可能凭空掉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是小透自己掏腰包买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们怎么都没想到这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为她老是傻笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会去注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管他什么情理巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她这样增加自己的困扰要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛不拿那些钱去买自己的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是交旅行基金呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她将来一定会吃大亏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.36,0:16:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她人生的百分之七十一定会在吃亏中度过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 昨天我参加读书会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在读书会之前 有个小孩去买了本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.04,0:16:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫做"世界的笨蛋故事全集"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个小孩很喜欢奇怪的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前也买了本"浓汤的宇宙"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们大家一起看了那本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.96,0:16:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中有一段是讲"世界最笨的旅人"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨旅人外出去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底有多笨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个旅人常一下子就上当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请借我点药钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他被镇上的人所骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗走了他的钱、衣服和鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.11,0:17:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妹妹生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没钱买种子种田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那个旅人因为笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到镇上的人说"谢谢你帮助我"时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.96,0:17:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还感动地说"祝你幸福 祝你幸福"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.47,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于 旅人全身赤裸 他感到很羞耻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以决定到森林里去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.47,0:17:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果这次他又碰到住在森林的魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.21,0:17:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔鬼因为想吃旅人的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讲了很多好话想骗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.32,0:17:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然旅人再度被骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.12,0:17:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先给了根脚 后来又给它一根手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:18:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后 旅人只剩下头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还是把眼睛给了最后那只魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.64,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只魔鬼一边吃着他的眼睛一边跟他说"谢谢"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.01,0:18:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并说"我有礼物要回送给你"把礼物放在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果竟是张写了"笨蛋"的纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.19,0:18:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是旅人他却哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 谢谢 这是我第一次收到的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.16,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高兴 我好高兴 谢谢你 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从失去眼睛的地方不停地流下眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后旅人就这样死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.82,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事讲完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.02,0:18:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朋友都很瞧不起旅人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我闭上了眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并想起了旅人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起了一直被骗到最后只剩一个头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还边说"谢谢"边哭的旅人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候我突然感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的是好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,损失、辛劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想这些都是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为旅人根本没想到这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许对别人来说他很笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但对我来说他一点都不笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对某人来说他可能很好骗 但我绝不会骗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.01,0:19:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的只是想让她高兴而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希呢？阿夹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还是觉得她很笨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭上眼睛 你们想到什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 早安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也陪你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没准备回礼给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就忍受那个笨蛋由希陪你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然啦 就算没有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可能也会玩得很高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能陪我去我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 我好高兴 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的拿你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹你一大早就好耀眼喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.71,0:21:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.88,0:21:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.01,0:21:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊～～阿夹欺负人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹说要跟我们一起去温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.66,0:21:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这趟大家一起去的"信步温泉之旅"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的好期待

